by xabbuh at 2017-05-02T03:32:23Z

The `FormExtension` class is part of the Twig bridge. Checking for the existence of a class from the Form component is not sufficient as the Form component in version 3.2 or higher may be used with an older version of the Twig bridge.

Also, you will then have to make sure that the Twig environment is passed to the Twig renderer engine (see the description of the deprecation in the extension class).

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by skalpa at 2017-05-03T14:50:11Z

