I changed the test and now check if `Symfony\Bridge\Twig\Extension\HttpKernelRuntime` exists (it was added by symfony/symfony@812fbb444f1d1e4cafff5876ce7b22d5b8d4adf8).

As for the renderer engine: I had already checked and the Twig environment is [already passed to the constructor](https://github.com/silexphp/Silex/blob/1b2f0394e28bb37cb3d86c84ba9a169b670c3fe9/src/Silex/Provider/TwigServiceProvider.php#L103).
